Kaya, para kay Mama,
pinatay din ni Iain Adair si Papa.

254
00:16:09,560 --> 00:16:10,440
Aba…

255
00:16:11,560 --> 00:16:13,000
-Hindi mali 'yon.
-Oo.

256
00:16:13,960 --> 00:16:15,120
