402
00:25:41,520 --> 00:25:42,880
Layas, parasito ka!

403
00:25:42,960 --> 00:25:45,400
Putang inang insekto ka!

404
00:25:45,480 --> 00:25:48,560
Bakit ka pa nag-uungkat? Tapos na 'yon.

405
00:25:48,640 --> 00:25:53,200
Nangyari na 'yon, at narito ka,
ibinabalik ang lahat.

406
00:25:53,280 --> 00:25:54,200
