417
00:26:41,920 --> 00:26:45,320
Pero, Pia, hindi ako sigurado
kung kumakain ka ng karne.

418
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,280
Kumakain ako.

419
00:26:47,440 --> 00:26:48,360
Sige.

420
00:26:51,120 --> 00:26:52,360
May iba pa ba, Ma?

421
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:54,880
Hindi, nakikita kong abala kayo.

422
00:26:54,960 --> 00:26:56,200
Si Stuart iyan.

423
00:26:57,640 --> 00:26:58,680
Anak ni Richard.

424
00:26:59,680 --> 00:27:00,760
Oo.

425
00:27:01,600 --> 00:27:03,320
Ano'ng ginagawa niyo?

426
00:27:08,640 --> 00:27:10,680
Gumagawa kami ng dokumentaryo

427
00:27:11,360 --> 00:27:13,800
tungkol sa nangyari.

428
00:27:15,840 --> 00:27:17,320
Kay Iain Adair, lahat.

429
00:27:18,120 --> 00:27:20,040
Hindi tungkol sa mangingitlog?

430
00:27:22,200 --> 00:27:23,040
Hindi.

431
00:27:26,800 --> 00:27:29,160
Sasabihin mo
ang ginawa niya sa tatay mo?

432
